  (https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32019R1241) as an
  important step towards GES for those D&rsquo;s), it should clearly explain why
  it is important for the descriptor that the MS adds measures linked to that
  legislation/policy.
</p>
